Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:04.70,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fill your empty heart with dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.04,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Spread your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:11.38,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,If you color your heart with the blowing wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.71,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}you will move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:17.88,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Get all the treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.18,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,while laughing out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.54,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Give them all out at a big party
